OL,3,CMen jailed after head-on 90mph crash
OL,4,Cwith unmarked police car
OL,6,FMiller, 54, of Sefton Park, Liverpool,
OL,7,Fwas "propelled from the back seat"
OL,8,Finto the centre console.
OL,10,FLiverpool Crown Court heard the
OL,11,Fpensioner was watching television
OL,12,Falone at his home in Anfield at around
OL,13,F10.15pm on 20 December 2024 when he
OL,14,F"heard a loud bang" as his window was
OL,15,Fsmashed.
OL,17,FThe three defendants then proceeded to
OL,18,Fenter through the broken window, with
OL,19,Fone of the men brandishing a hammer
OL,20,Ftowards the pensioner while demanding
OL,21,Fmoney.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
