CT,2,C
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F395A1753213035
OL,3,CMen jailed after head-on 90mph crash
OL,4,Cwith unmarked police car
OL,6,FHelen Chenery, prosecuting, told the
OL,7,Fcourt the pensioner ultimately handed
OL,8,Fover #240 from his pocket as a result
OL,9,Fof the threats, while another of the
OL,10,Foffenders took the keys to his #25,000
OL,11,FJaguar car from his briefcase.
OL,13,FAll three then climbed back out of the
OL,14,Fhome via the broken window and sped
OL,15,Faway inside the vehicle.
OL,17,FIn a statement read to the court on
OL,18,Fhis behalf, the victim said: "Prior to
OL,19,Fthe incident, I was an independent 76-
OL,20,Fyear-old man who lived on his own. My
OL,21,Fhome is meant to be a safe space.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
