PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F395A1753213035
OL,3,CMen jailed after head-on 90mph crash
OL,4,Cwith unmarked police car
OL,6,F"I knew, because of my age, that I was
OL,7,Funable to fight. These males entered
OL,8,Fmy home, where I'm meant to feel safe,
OL,9,Fand made me feel vulnerable and scared.
OL,11,F"I have worked hard all my life. This
OL,12,Fhas affected my family greatly, to the
OL,13,Fpoint where they want me to relocate
OL,14,Fto Southampton to ensure that I'm safe
OL,15,Fand that nothing like this will happen
OL,16,Fagain.
OL,18,F"I have a large classic toy car
OL,19,Fcollection. A lot of these were bought
OL,20,Fas presents by my wife, who passed
OL,21,Faway a few years ago.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
