PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F395A1753213035
OL,3,CMen jailed after head-on 90mph crash
OL,4,Cwith unmarked police car
OL,6,F"A lot of these were damaged by the
OL,7,Foffenders breaking in through the
OL,8,Fwindow. This has caused a lot of
OL,9,Fheartache for me."
OL,11,FOne of the Merseyside Police PCs
OL,12,Finvolved in the crash reported
OL,13,Fsuffering "bruising and pain" as a
OL,14,Fresult, while the other will be left
OL,15,Fwith permanent scarring as a result of
OL,16,Fa cut to his hip.
OL,18,FO'Connor, who admitted robbery, theft,
OL,19,Fdangerous driving, driving while
OL,20,Fdisqualified, theft and going equipped
OL,21,Ffor theft, was jailed for nine years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
