OL,3,CMen jailed after head-on 90mph crash
OL,4,Cwith unmarked police car
OL,6,FWhile Miller pleaded guilty to robbery
OL,7,Fand theft, and was jailed for eight
OL,8,Fyears and one month.
OL,10,FSentencing, Recorder Richard Pratt KC
OL,11,Fsaid: "It is not possible to say which
OL,12,Fof you held the hammer, neither does
OL,13,Fthat matter. Whichever one of you did
OL,14,Fnot have the hammer plainly knew that
OL,15,Fthe other one did.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
