PN,39508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F395A1753213035
OL,3,CMen jailed after head-on 90mph crash
OL,4,Cwith unmarked police car
OL,6,F"It was you, O'Connor, who was driving
OL,7,Fthe vehicle. The vehicle was driven in
OL,8,Fa highly dangerous way at speed with
OL,9,Fits lights switched off. A collision
OL,10,Fwas almost inevitable, and it
OL,11,Fhappened. Those police officers
OL,12,Fsuffered injury, both physical and
OL,13,Fpsychological, while they were doing
OL,14,Fnothing more than their duty.
OL,16,FHe continued: "It is clear that his
OL,17,Findependence and pride was shattered
OL,18,Fby your actions on this night. The
OL,19,Fonly real mitigation that can be
OL,20,Fadvanced on either of your behalves is
OL,21,Fthe fact that you pleaded guilty."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
