OL,3,CMen jailed after head-on 90mph crash
OL,4,Cwith unmarked police car
OL,6,FO'Connor's criminal record shows 17
OL,7,Fprevious convictions for 32 offences,
OL,8,Fincluding burglary, aggravated vehicle
OL,9,Ftaking and dangerous driving.
OL,11,FPeter White, defending, said on his
OL,12,Fbehalf: "There is no justification for
OL,13,FMr O'Connor's conduct. He tells me
OL,14,Fthat this period of his life was
OL,15,Fentirely dominated by drink and drugs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
