OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F395A1753213035
OL,3,CMen jailed after head-on 90mph crash
OL,4,Cwith unmarked police car
OL,6,F"He had a chaotic lifestyle and was
OL,7,Facting wholly inappropriately and not
OL,8,Fthinking straight. He tells me that he
OL,9,Fhad a long term relationship which
OL,10,Fcame to an end in 2018. He lost
OL,11,Fcontact with his young son. Since
OL,12,Fthen, his offending has massively
OL,13,Fescalated. He has been in that vicious
OL,14,Fcycle, in and out of prison and doing
OL,15,Fanything to fund his addiction.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
