PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F395A1753213035
OL,3,CMen jailed after head-on 90mph crash
OL,4,Cwith unmarked police car
OL,6,F"He has heard the consequences of his
OL,7,Factions. He is more than aware that
OL,8,Fsomeone could have easily died in that
OL,9,Fhorrendous piece of dangerous driving,
OL,10,Fand it is only through good fortune
OL,11,Fthat he is not facing a more serious
OL,12,Foffence."
OL,14,FMiller has 40 prior convictions for
OL,15,F112 offences dating back to 1987,
OL,16,Fincluding 54 for theft related matters.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
